</h2> <img src="images/shepards.png" width="400px" height= "300px" alt="Rescipe_item">
                            <div class="receipe-duration">
                                <h6>Prep Time: 15  mins</h6>
                                <h6>Cook time: 60  mins</h6>

                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

